{"info": {"_postman_id": "beijixing-ai-postman-collection-v1.0", "name": "北极星AI - 核心API测试集合", "description": "# 北极星AI Postman测试集合\n\n**版本**: v1.0  \n**更新时间**: 2026-05-20  \n**适用环境**: 生产环境 (http://your-server:8080)\n\n## 📋 使用说明\n\n### 前置条件\n1. 应用已成功部署并启动\n2. 可访问 `http://your-server:8080/actuator/health` 返回UP状态\n\n### 环境变量配置\n在Postman中设置以下环境变量：\n```\nbase_url = http://your-server:8080\nusername = admin\npassword = your-password\n```\n\n### 测试流程建议\n1. **健康检查** → 验证服务可用性\n2. **用户认证** → 获取JWT Token\n3. **核心业务API** → 带Token访问各模块接口\n4. **评论抓取API** → Phase 3新增功能测试\n\n---\n\n## 🧪 测试用例列表\n\n| 序号 | 模块 | 接口 | 方法 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 系统 | /actuator/health | GET | 健康检查 |\n| 2 | 认证 | /api/v1/auth/login | POST | 用户登录获取Token |\n| 3 | 用户 | /api/v1/user/info | GET | 获取当前用户信息 |\n| 4 | 合规 | /api/v1/compliance/sensitive-word/check | POST | 敏感词检测 |\n| 5 | 合规 | /api/v1/compliance/rate-limit/check | POST | 频率限制检查 |\n| 6 | 社交 | /api/v1/social/crawl/comments | POST | 评论抓取（Phase 3） |\n| 7 | 社交 | /api/v1/social/crawl/targets | GET | 查询抓取目标池 |\n| 8 | 内容 | /api/v1/content/publish | POST | 发布内容 |\n| 9 | 监控 | /api/v1/monitor/metrics | GET | 系统指标 |\n\n---\n\n**作者**: 北极星AI团队  \n**许可证**: 内部使用", "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"}, "variable": [{"key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string"}, {"key": "jwt_token", "value": "", "type": "string"}], "item": [{"name": "🏥 1. 健康检查", "item": [{"name": "1.1 应用健康检查", "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["// 测试脚本：验证健康检查响应", "pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {", "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);", "});", "", "// 验证返回JSON格式", "pm.test(\"Response is JSON\", function () {", "    pm.response.to.be.json;", "});", "", "// 验证status字段为UP", "pm.test(\"Application status is UP\", function () {", "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();", "    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.eql(\"UP\");", "});", "", "// 输出组件状态到控制台", "if (pm.response.json().components) {", "    console.log(\"\\n=== 组件状态 ===\");", "    Object.keys(pm.response.json().components).forEach(function(key) {", "        console.log(key + \": \" + pm.response.json().components[key].status);", "    });", "}"], "type": "text/javascript"}}], "request": {"method": "GET", "header": [{"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}], "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/actuator/health", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["actuator", "health"]}, "description": "检查应用整体健康状态，包括数据库、Redis等组件"}}]}, {"name": "🔐 2. 用户认证", "item": [{"name": "2.1 用户登录（获取JWT Token）", "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["// 测试脚本：验证登录成功并提取Token", "pm.test(\"Login successful - Status 200\", function () {", "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);", "});", "", "pm.test(\"Response has token\", function () {", "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();", "    pm.expect(jsonData.code).to.eql(200);", "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('token');", "    ", "    // 将token保存到环境变量，供后续请求使用", "    if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.token) {", "        pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', 'Bearer ' + jsonData.data.token);", "        console.log('\\n✅ JWT Token已保存');", "    }", "});"], "type": "text/javascript"}}], "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]}, "description": "用户登录接口，成功后返回JWT Token用于后续认证"}}, {"name": "2.2 刷新Token", "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}, {"key": "Authorization", "value": "{{jwt_token}}"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "refresh"]}, "description": "使用refresh_token刷新access_token"}}]}, {"name": "👤 3. 用户管理", "item": [{"name": "3.1 获取当前用户信息", "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test(\"Get user info success\", function () {", "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);", "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();", "    pm.expect(jsonData.code).to.eql(200);", "});"], "type": "text/javascript"}}], "request": {"method": "GET", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "{{jwt_token}}"}], "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/user/info", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "user", "info"]}, "description": "获取当前登录用户的详细信息"}}]}, {"name": "🛡️ 4. 合规服务", "item": [{"name": "4.1 敏感词过滤检测", "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test(\"Sensitive word check\", function () {", "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);", "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();", "    console.log('\\n检测结果:', JSON.stringify(jsonData, null, 2));", "});"], "type": "text/javascript"}}], "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "{{jwt_token}}"}, {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n    \"text\": \"这是一条正常的测试消息\",\n    \"platformCode\": \"DOUYIN\"\n}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/compliance/sensitive-word/check", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "compliance", "sensitive-word", "check"]}, "description": "测试敏感词过滤功能（正常文本）"}}, {"name": "4.2 敏感词检测 - 包含敏感词", "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "{{jwt_token}}"}, {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n    \"text\": \"这条消息包含违禁词汇如赌博、色情等\",\n    \"platformCode\": \"DOUYIN\"\n}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/compliance/sensitive-word/check", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "compliance", "sensitive-word", "check"]}, "description": "测试包含敏感词的文本（应被过滤）"}}, {"name": "4.3 频率限制检查", "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test(\"Rate limit check\", function () {", "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);", "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();", "    console.log('频率限制结果:', JSON.stringify(jsonData, null, 2));", "});"], "type": "text/javascript"}}], "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "{{jwt_token}}"}, {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n    \"accountId\": \"test-account-001\",\n    \"targetUserId\": \"target-user-001\",\n    \"platformCode\": \"DOUYIN\"\n}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/compliance/rate-limit/check", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "compliance", "rate-limit", "check"]}, "description": "检查是否可以发送私信（基于令牌桶算法）"}}]}, {"name": "🕷️ 5. 评论抓取 (Phase 3)", "item": [{"name": "5.1 抖音评论抓取", "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test(\"Douyin comment crawl initiated\", function () {", "    // 注意：此接口可能需要有效的OAuth Token", "    pm.response.to.have.status.oneOf([200, 202, 400]);", "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();", "    console.log('抖音抓取结果:', JSON.stringify(jsonData, null, 2));", "});"], "type": "text/javascript"}}], "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "{{jwt_token}}"}, {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n    \"platformCode\": \"DOUYIN\",\n    \"targetUrl\": \"https://www.douyin.com/video/xxxxx\",\n    \"options\": {\n        \"pageSize\": 20,\n        \"maxPages\": 5,\n        \"includeReplies\": true,\n        \"sortType\": \"TIME_DESC\"\n    }\n}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/social/crawl/comments", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "social", "crawl", "comments"]}, "description": "发起抖音视频评论抓取任务"}}, {"name": "5.2 小红书笔记评论抓取", "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "{{jwt_token}}"}, {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n    \"platformCode\": \"XIAOHONGSHU\",\n    \"targetUrl\": \"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/xxxxx\",\n    \"options\": {\n        \"pageSize\": 30,\n        \"maxPages\": 10,\n        \"includeReplies\": true,\n        \"sortType\": \"TIME_DESC\"\n    }\n}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/social/crawl/comments", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "social", "crawl", "comments"]}, "description": "发起小红书笔记评论抓取任务"}}, {"name": "5.3 查询抓取目标池", "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test(\"Get crawl targets list\", function () {", "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);", "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();", "    if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.records) {", "        console.log('\\n目标数量:', jsonData.data.total);", "    }", "});"], "type": "text/javascript"}}], "request": {"method": "GET", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "{{jwt_token}}"}], "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/social/crawl/targets?page=1&size=10", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "social", "crawl", "targets"], "query": [{"key": "page", "value": "1"}, {"key": "size", "value": "10"}], "description": "分页查询自定义抓取目标列表"}}]}]}, {"name": "📝 6. 内容管理", "item": [{"name": "6.1 创建内容草稿", "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "{{jwt_token}}"}, {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n    \"title\": \"测试内容标题\",\n    \"content\": \"这是测试内容正文...\",\n    \"contentType\": \"TEXT\",\n    \"platformCodes\": [\"DOUYIN\", \"XIAOHONGSHU\"]\n}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/content/draft", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "content", "draft"]}, "description": "创建内容草稿（待发布）"}}]}, {"name": "📊 7. 系统监控", "item": [{"name": "7.1 获取系统指标", "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test(\"Get system metrics\", function () {", "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);", "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();", "    console.log('\\n系统指标:', JSON.stringify(jsonData, null, 2));", "});"], "type": "text/javascript"}}], "request": {"method": "GET", "header": [{"key": "Authorization", "value": "{{jwt_token}}"}], "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/monitor/metrics/system", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "monitor", "metrics", "system"]}, "description": "获取系统性能指标（CPU、内存、磁盘等）"}}]}]}